description:
A wonderful pair of personalised map cufflinks, capturing those cherished locations that hold an extra special memory making them the perfect gift.

The locations are what its all about. Here are some ideas to get the ball rolling, remember you can choose locations from all over the world, providing you stick to our above guidelines, of course!

How about their home town, University city, the place where you first met each other, where you got engaged, married or honeymooned?

All our maps are authentic and therefore will differ slightly from the photograph in colour, scale and age. Please do not use postcodes or anything that is unlikely to appear on a vintage map such hotels,  a local monument or a private property. If our guidelines are not followed, it can slow down the production time of your item and can risk your order being delayed, so we do advise opting for a city, town or large village where possible. If we cannot find your specific location, our team will choose a map to cover the area of it using their knowledge of our map range to make the very best product we can.

Each pair of cufflinks comes in their very own Ellie Ellie cufflink box, for keeping them as safe as houses when they're not being worn!

title: Personalised Vintage Map Pocket Watch - Personalise With Your Choice Of Location
description:
A beautiful daily reminder of a special memory, our personalised map pocket watches feature a personalised front framing a segment of vintage map.

Each watch is customised here at Ellie Ellie HQ in Sussex using original vintage maps. 

All our maps are authentic and therefore will differ slightly from the photograph in colour, scale and age. Please do not use postcodes or anything that is unlikely to appear on a vintage map such hotels,  a local monument or a private property. If our guidelines are not followed, it can slow down the production time of your item and can risk your order being delayed, so we do advise opting for a city, town or large village where possible. If we cannot find your specific location, our team will choose a map to cover the area of it using their knowledge of our map range to make the very best product we can.


Perfect gift to a husband-to-be to make sure he turns up at the right place.. and on time!

title: Lucky Sixpence for Your Christmas Pudding, To Bring Good Luck and Weath For The New Year
description:
The act of placing a sixpence into the Christmas pudding has been a Christmas tradition for over 100 years. Placed in the pudding when cooking, the tradition believes that whoever finds the sixpence in their piece of the pudding on Christmas day is thought to have wealth and luck over the next year.

Design and printed by Ellie Ellie in Sussex (UK) our wooden card includes one sixpence along with the instructions: 'Add me to your Christmas pudding and get every family to give it a stir. Whoever finds me in their pudding on Christmas day will enjoy wealth and good luck the year to come'.

A wonderful gift that be brought out year after year in the run up to Christmas, a great activity for all the family to do.

Sixpence dates will vary.

PLEASE NOTE THIS IS NOT SUITABLE FOR CHILDREN - SMALL ITEM IS A CHOCKING HAZARD.

Laser engraved wood.

Real vintage sixpence.

7.5 x 4.7cm

title: Map Personalised Wine Bottle Stopper
description:
This personalised map bottle stopper is a beautiful and innovative piece of tableware that makes a thoughtful gift for family, friends, couples or colleagues!

The stopper is double-sided, allowing scope for two separate locations that really mean something to the recipient.

They are great for anyone who loves a tipple or two! The stoppers are suitable for a variety of bottles, not just wine. A great personalised gift for a scotch or whiskey lover too!

The locations are what it is all about; how about the recipient's home town, where their kids were born, University city, the place where you first met each other, where you got engaged, married or honeymooned?

All our maps are authentic and therefore will differ slightly from the photograph in colour, scale and age. Please do not use postcodes or anything that is unlikely to appear on a vintage map such hotels,  a local monument or a private property. If our guidelines are not followed, it can slow down the production time of your item and can risk your order being delayed, so we do advise opting for a city, town or large village where possible. If we cannot find your specific location, our team will choose a map to cover the area of it using their knowledge of our map range to make the very best product we can.


All of our bottle stoppers come in their very own Ellie Ellie gift box, for that finishing touch.

Is it a gift? We've got the perfect finishing touch, our Ellie Ellie Turqouise Giftbag is the ideal way to make sure your gift is extra special.

Handmade from vintage maps and atlases.

Bottle stop is made from zinc alloy.

title: Personalised Vintage Map Choose Your Location Pendant Necklace
description:
A wonderful personalised map pendant to capture those special memories that hold a special story in your heart. Made using authentic recycled vintage maps!

Each pendant is handmade here at Ellie Ellie HQ in Sussex using authentic recycled vintage maps. The personalisation ideas are endless and entirely up to you!

Remember you can choose locations from all over the world (providing you stick to our above guidelines, of course!). The locations are what its all about. Here are some ideas to get the ball rolling:

title: Personalised Vintage Map Oval Necklace Pendant - Choose Your Own Location
description:
Our bestselling Personalised Map Oval Pendant is the perfect way to capture a place close to you. A great gift for anniversaries, weddings, birthdays.

A wonderful way of capturing those cherished locations and the memories they hold. The perfect for anniversaries, weddings and birthdays.

Each oval shaped map pendant is handmade here at Ellie Ellie HQ in Sussex using authentic re-cycled vintage maps- the personalisation ideas are endless and entirely up to you! You can choose locations from all over the world (providing you stick to our guidelines, of course!)

All our maps are authentic and therefore will differ slightly from the photograph in colour, scale and age. Please do not use postcodes or anything that is unlikely to appear on a vintage map such hotels,  a local monument or a private property. If we cannot find your specific location, our team will choose a map to cover the area of it using their knowledge of our map range to make the very best product we can.
